1 (7) For each expenditure described in subdivision (5), a
2 description of how the expenditure aligns with at least one (1)
3 priority specified in the nonprofit hospital's community health
4 needs assessment filed under 26 U.S.C. 501(r).
5 (8) An estimate of the financial value of all state and local tax
